== RUGWABIZA Valentine ==
RUGWABIZA Valentine  wavutse kuya 25 Nyakanga 1963  ni umunyarwandakazi

akaba n' umunyapolitike uhagarariye u  '''''[[Rwanda Nziza|Rwanda]] '''''mu muryango wabibumbye kuva mu mwaka wa 2016.

== Ibyo yakoze ==
Rugwabiza  Valentine kuva mu mwaka wa 2005 kugeza muri 2015 yabaye umuyobozi mukuru wungirije w'umuryango 

w'ubucuruzi ku Isi<ref>https://www.un.org/africarenewal/magazine/april-2021/rwanda-un-vaccine-equity-inclusion-peace-and-gender-equality-top-our-priorities</ref>. mbere yaho gato yabaye uhagarariye u '''''[[Rwanda]] '''''uhoraho muri [[ONU|Loni]] i [[Ubusuwisi|Geneve]] na Ambasaderi 

udasanzwe mu [[Ubusuwisi|Busuwis]]<nowiki/>i. mugihe yari Ambasaderi yabaye umuhuza bikorwa w 'itsinda nyafurika ry'amasaderi muri<ref>https://africanscholars.yale.edu/people/hon-valentine-rugwabiza</ref>

(WTO). kandi yari umwe mubagize<ref>https://www.oecd.org/dac/aft/Session%207%20-%20Valentine%20Rugwabiza.pdf</ref> akanama ku ubukungu nimibereho myiza mubiro  bya Perezida wu [[Rwanda Nziza|Rwanda]] i '' '''[[Kigali]] '''''

== Umwihariko ==
Ambasaderi  Rugwabiza Valentine  ni umunyamuryango washinze ihuriro ry'abikorera kugiti cyabo mu [[Rwanda Nziza|Rwanda]] 

ishyirahamwe ry'abagore ba Rwiyemezamirimo bo mu Rwanda<ref>https://africanscholars.yale.edu/people/hon-valentine-rugwabiza</ref> hamwe n'abagore babayobozi bo mu [[Rwanda]].

Ambasaderi Rugwabiza  yabaye umwe mubagize Inama y'ubuyobozi muri [[Kaminuza y'u Rwanda|Kaminuza]]<ref>https://www.concordia.net/community/ambassador-valentine-rugwabiza/</ref> y'umuryango 

w' abibumbye ishinzwe Amahoro.  Rugwabiza  amaze imyaka irenga mirongo itatu akora kubibazo

by'iterambere ry'Africa ndetse ni isi yose haba mu bigo  no munzego za Leta.<ref>https://unitar.org/about/unitar/governance/board-trustees/valentine-rugwabiza</ref>

